com.activeorm.database

Class DbTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.activeorm.database.DbTable

  • public class DbTable
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is developed for give support in creation and execution of queries, and offers methods for executing DML and QL instructions. It also has method for helping the use of queries.
